WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Look, what do you want and do not waste my time?

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
I have a real emergency to deal with.

3
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Sir.

4
00:00:08.130 --> 00:00:11.130
My boyfriend has been comatose for the past three years

5
00:00:11.130 --> 00:00:13.130
and he really needs to continue his treatments

6
00:00:13.130 --> 00:00:15.130
but I had to drop out of school to take care of him

7
00:00:15.130 --> 00:00:18.129
and then I ran out of money and the hospital kicked me out.

8
00:00:18.129 --> 00:00:21.129
Ah, I remember that.

9
00:00:21.129 --> 00:00:25.129
I saw an email about a girl who dropped out of MIT to take care of her boyfriend.

10
00:00:25.129 --> 00:00:26.129
Is that you?

11
00:00:26.129 --> 00:00:27.129
Yes, that's me.

12
00:00:27.129 --> 00:00:28.129
It was declined.

13
00:00:28.129 --> 00:00:30.789
What?

14
00:00:30.789 --> 00:00:31.789
What happened?

15
00:00:31.789 --> 00:00:36.789
First, based off what you wrote, the patient is your boyfriend, not your husband.

16
00:00:36.789 --> 00:00:43.920
And you say you dropped out of MIT to take on various jobs to fund his treatment?

17
00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:48.240
Yes, I sacrificed everything for him.

18
00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:50.590
Why is that bad?

19
00:00:50.590 --> 00:00:53.590
Because your little sob story is fake.

20
00:00:53.590 --> 00:00:54.590
It's too unbelievable.

21
00:00:54.590 --> 00:00:56.590
No one would do that in real life.

22
00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:58.590
It's true, please.

23
00:00:58.590 --> 00:00:59.590
Sir, I swear, it's all true.

24
00:00:59.590 --> 00:01:00.590
Every word of it.

25
00:01:00.590 --> 00:01:03.590
Miss, let go of me. This is highly inappropriate.

26
00:01:03.590 --> 00:01:08.000
We need this opportunity for him to survive, sir.

27
00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.000
You don't understand.

28
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Get out of my way and leave me alone.

29
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.000
I'm in a hurry to find someone.

30
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Sir, please wait.

31
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.540
Stop lying.

32
00:01:17.540 --> 00:01:23.540
Alright, if you insist on continuing, I will press you with charges of fraud.

33
00:01:23.540 --> 00:01:26.540
And we will investigate your application.

34
00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:27.540
Good day, ma'am.

